{"tid":1097364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【丁權覆核案．拆局】郭卓堅明贏實輸　原居民「輸粒糖贏間廠」","createTime":"2019-04-08T10:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T12:53:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5258dcdeba1f92734b8ffd51685c37144294c1","tid":1097364,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2650783/org/7448675261b02ca012686f394aae6126.jpg/JvzK7aQ4Byk32lytA6aaJuZ6md9x7btLjMp-LIzKfiw?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2650783%2Forg%2F7448675261b02ca012686f394aae6126.jpg%2FJvzK7aQ4Byk32lytA6aaJuZ6md9x7btLjMp-LIzKfiw%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=13cfe06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅於2015年就丁屋政策提出司法覆核，要求取消新界原居民享有的丁權。案件於去年12月開審，歷時多月後於今日（8日）宣判，郭卓堅部份勝訴，如以私人協約方式（Private Treaty Grant）和換地批出的丁權，屬於違憲，意即丁屋權本身合法，如用公家地就不合法。<br />\n<br />\n雖然法官裁定申請人郭卓堅部分勝訴，但今次結果卻首次確立了丁權受《基本法》保障，結束了丁權是否屬於新界原居民合法傳統權的多年爭論。而參考過去五年數字，在私人土地批建丁屋的個案均佔逾8成，以私人協約方式和換地批出的丁權，則只佔少數。換言之，今次裁決難以真正搖動現行的丁屋制度，原居民在官司中可謂「輸粒糖贏間廠」。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行的措施，若原居民有意興建丁屋，若建屋地屬官地，要由私人協約方式（Private Treaty Grant）批出；私人土地則要申請免費建屋牌照（Free Building Licence），亦可以換地（Exchange）批出小型屋宇契約。<br />\n<br />\n首次確認丁權受《基本法》保障 判決有利原居民<br />\n<br />\n「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅於2015年提出司法覆核，要求取消新界原居民享有丁權權利。根據高等法院頒布的判詞第130條，法官裁定在私人土地上建屋的丁權受《基本法》保障，不過，以私人協約方式和換地批出的丁權，則屬違憲。<br />\n<br />\n過去丁權爭議不斷，不少原居民堅持丁權是他們的「合法傳統權益」之一。然而，根據《基本法》第40條，當中只列明了新界原居民的「合法傳統權益」受保護，並未有明確指出丁屋政策屬原居民「合法傳統權益」之一；反對丁權人士則認為丁權只是當年原居民和港英政府的協議，指丁屋政策根本不是原居民傳統，遑論是「合法傳統權益」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，今次的裁判卻指出，以免費建屋牌照批的丁權，均屬原居民「合法傳統權益」，故今次的判決，首次承認了丁權可與《基本法》掛勾，反而強化了原居民建丁屋的法律理據。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2649793/org/264cfbc8a07ada223c43c3820ce85ed9.jpg/_5Ud6w-tZ1WL5kaafhIXlikGiTzT0tcYLaHhVS2h4VU?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2649793%2Forg%2F264cfbc8a07ada223c43c3820ce85ed9.jpg%2F_5Ud6w-tZ1WL5kaafhIXlikGiTzT0tcYLaHhVS2h4VU%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=a16a7aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n私地獲批申建丁屋佔逾8成 受判決影響丁屋僅佔少數<br />\n<br />\n因此，今次判決中值得留意是，雖然法官裁定以官地建丁屋違憲，但原居民利用私人土地建丁屋的權利，則未有影響。<br />\n<br />\n翻查發展局數據，在2013至2017年間成功獲批的丁屋申請個案，均以免費建屋牌照批出的佔多數，五年間佔逾8成。相反，若以私人協約及換地政式批出的丁屋，則只佔最多15%及3%。換言之，即使今次結果裁定申請人郭卓堅部分勝訴，但受影響的丁屋其實只屬少數，但佔多數批出丁屋的方法，仍然合法，更是受到《基本法》保障的原居民「合法傳統權益」。<br />\n<br />\n同時，根據地政總署數字，2008至17年間正接獲的丁屋申請數字，由1,810減至1,129宗，但正處理的申請數字卻不斷增加，十年間由7,613宗增至8,548宗，增幅達一成，反映當中或有不少原居民苦候多年，仍然等待政府批出土地建屋，故以私人協約批出的土地只佔少數。鄉議局執行議員林國昌今日在庭外更承認，私人協約方式或以換地方式批出的丁權，是舊時做法，現時已幾乎「絕迹」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2649451/org/45e2e8bdb9608c4d6a139a3f3a3f7cb5.jpg/5QAxuVD7m2hMRnKmcHVYBfugeup7gHsrYeyrh2Hsq4c?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2649451%2Forg%2F45e2e8bdb9608c4d6a139a3f3a3f7cb5.jpg%2F5QAxuVD7m2hMRnKmcHVYBfugeup7gHsrYeyrh2Hsq4c%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=040c2982&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e3b4bb8c2eb5b65c74a27f26973d5ac988bb3a6","tid":1097364,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"鬼王郭卓堅不嬲係故意輸官司派牌比政府"},{"pid":"4de2d986448af68a4d38d2856adad6ac053727d6","tid":1097364,"uid":33808,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7e3b4bb8c2eb5b65c74a27f26973d5ac988bb3a6","tid":1097364,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"鬼王郭卓堅不嬲係故意輸官司派牌比政府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:37:27.000Z","msg":"又來全世界係鬼"},{"pid":"f0188dac3bd31cd33ab0b420714ec259680e7b53","tid":1097364,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/609459/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/609459/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n呵呵"},{"pid":"262fb004afea7a2fb65c0e50bbc29ad4649301ce","tid":1097364,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:57:50.000Z","msg":"原居民稱無輸卻被「封後門」 判詞或有利釋放900公頃丁屋預留地 <br />\n<br />\n高等法院為丁權司法覆核案頒下判詞，指以私人協約或換地方式批出的丁權違憲。本土研究社成員黃肇鴻指，以此2種方法批出的丁權，均牽涉官地，前者是原居民以優惠價，向政府購買土地建丁屋，後者是以其私人土地，向政府交換地點較好的官地建丁屋。翻查資料，<span style=\"color: red;\">2012年任發展局局長的陳茂波指，全港有約1,200公頃官地預留建丁屋</span>，扣除道路和斜坡等後，尚有約930公頃可發展。黃指出，法庭為官地變丁屋「封後門」，意味該930公頃可釋放作其他用途；保守估算當中約34公頃，適合建公營房屋，但擔心未來有更多「擴丁」情況出現。 <br />\n<br />\n黃肇鴻又說，<span style=\"color: red;\">鄉議局聲稱已很久沒有用優惠價買地或以換地方式建丁屋，說法不正確。事實上，政府一直有批出官地，予原居民建丁屋；自1972年丁屋政策實施至今，批出官地與私人地建丁屋的比例約為3：7，其中2016年就約有100宗以賣官地或換地方式建丁屋的個案。</span>他指政府由1972年至今，從無公佈過批出多少面積的官地建丁屋，做法不透明。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨議員尹兆堅亦認為，鄉議局在丁權案「明贏實輸」、「極之影響深遠」，「<span style=\"color: red;\">過去丁權好長久以來，其實好靠私人協約方式嘅土地，同埋換地嘅方式進行，過去咁多年以來、由1972年至2018年，用私人協約方式嘅用地係有25.2%，用換地嘅就有8.5%，即係加埋就有33.7%</span>，（鄉議局執委）林國昌話其實唔多、影響好細，我就覺得唔係，因為數字佔咗成三分一」。尹又指，政府今後毋須再預留900多公頃官地建丁屋，已失去藉口以千億公帑硬推大部份巿民反對的「明日大嶼」填海計劃。 <br />\n<br />\n新界西立法會議員朱凱廸認為，判決是新界私人地主的勝利，法庭沒有考慮不少新界土地被有勢力人士或私人地產商「套丁」的情況，「可以起丁屋嘅私人地，係大量被私人地產商控制。今次判決係為私人地主，繼續控制丁屋發展打咗基礎」，並擔心政府藉此拖延檢討丁屋政策。他又說，鄉議局可能仗勢要求政府強化丁屋政策，助長地主牟利，促鄉議局反省原居民是否繼續享有建丁屋的權利，是丁屋只屬少數人利益。"},{"pid":"580fade7c1935c80f392010dfe62d1bc782b1623","tid":1097364,"uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"即係你條村既地，比丁權無問題<br />\n<br />\n但條村爆棚就唔好意思啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知好多村都問政府拎地擴村"},{"pid":"a3f71d743b2d879c3c113153472620ee6f917ceb","tid":1097364,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047f33363483b101ab1960651410feb295f4dd8c","tid":1097364,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1543ae3e6c77dd1c116fb953b393b795d8285b4d","tid":1097364,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"應該條係私家地用完就冇，睇落好似封左頂"},{"pid":"a09304d4bb3efe2da752b18c7d390e23dc495297","tid":1097364,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"普天之下 莫非共土"},{"pid":"79b5cb41f606213333bca620306567b647eb8e9b","tid":1097364,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f0ea83cf2afdae6a18ad6c438963ba4a3e37f7b","tid":1097364,"uid":72020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"郭卓堅會唔會俾圍村佬斬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f673a3740aec55b095faf48ccda47f1efe49aebb","tid":1097364,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"政府不需再預留土地，咁都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6272750e0704f716d3343b679598313bf12ed976","tid":1097364,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b02ed8839fd92418089e0a892cb49e939b4798","tid":1097364,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">政府今後毋須再預留900多公頃官地建丁屋，已失去藉口以千億公帑硬推大部份巿民反對的「明日大嶼」填海計劃</span><br />\n<br />\n係咪真先?"},{"pid":"2267fdf3365bf5a518bbf12503975c6707bd40ff","tid":1097364,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"愛國受基本法保障又唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家係共產黨保障你免鬥地主喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0059d3c523643363a4f0dd301c5225ffc43e97","tid":1097364,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f673a3740aec55b095faf48ccda47f1efe49aebb","tid":1097364,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"政府不需再預留土地，咁都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"偽命題黎，跟本無留"},{"pid":"c52a87dffd39d7221882245754bad1b5928cf56a","tid":1097364,"uid":51183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6b02ed8839fd92418089e0a892cb49e939b4798","tid":1097364,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">政府今後毋須再預留900多公頃官地建丁屋，已失去藉口以千億公帑硬推大部份巿民反對的「明日大嶼」填海計劃</span><br />\n<br />\n係咪真先?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"係人都知明日大罪係送錢比中國<br />\n無地係籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6960df485308f908d01ae01c2fb0cebb1c2f3f3","tid":1097364,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:39:20.000Z","msg":"皇法加護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a98fc17fe576456447d59ca56d77a6cc448e8b","tid":1097364,"uid":86980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"郭卓堅一個人, 在沒有任何議員薪津嘅支援下, 佢所做到嘅嘢<br />\n已經超越咗擁有律師, 大狀, 教授, 其他專業人士坐鎮的民主黨和公民黨<br />\n究竟泛民係做不到? 定係刻意唔做?<br />\n邊個先係人? 邊個先係鬼? 我真係分唔到"},{"pid":"0f229e9fe35ec24780b26503668f42e28215a3ca","tid":1097364,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a98fc17fe576456447d59ca56d77a6cc448e8b","tid":1097364,"uid":86980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"郭卓堅一個人, 在沒有任何議員薪津嘅支援下, 佢所做到嘅嘢<br />\n已經超越咗擁有律師, 大狀, 教授, 其他專業人士坐鎮的民主黨和公民黨<br />\n究竟泛民係做不到? 定係刻意唔做?<br />\n邊個先係人? 邊個先係鬼? 我真係分唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"李柱銘打"}]}